history.content:
How will the enrollment with time conflict work? If I have two online classes at the same time but they both allow time conflict enrollments, will they have any final exam accommodations? Also, can I directly enroll in these two classes in Calcentral just as usual, or do I need to do something special? 

I would really appreciate it if anyone can share their time conflict enrollment experiences! Thanks!
